query:
SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, u.superAdmin, ul.id as license_id, ul.userId as licensed_user_id
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN user_licenses ul ON u.id = ul.userId AND ul.isActive = 1
WHERE u.tenantId = (SELECT id FROM tenants LIMIT 1)
ORDER BY u.id;
